## 6. Architecture Principles

* REST-based API design
* Clear separation of concerns:

  * Models
  * Controllers
  * Middleware
  * Routes
* JavaScript-first (no TypeScript)
* Secure-by-default approach
* Modular and extensible design

---

## 7. Summary

The chosen tech stack prioritizes:

* Developer productivity
* Simplicity and clarity
* Security and maintainability
* Easy future extensibility

This stack is well-suited for an internal professional dashboard used daily in a Chartered Accountant firm.
